                  </div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Real-time Tax Calculation
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Enhanced UX with automatic tax updates based on zip code input
                  </p>
